---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';

const lastUpdated = "January 1, 2025";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="AITS Genesis Cookie Policy — what cookies we use, why, and how to manage your preferences."
>
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Legal", href: "#" }, { label: "Cookie Policy" }]} />
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mt-6">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p>This Cookie Policy explains how AITS Genesis uses cookies and similar tracking technologies on <strong>aitsgenesis.com</strong>. By using our website, you consent to our use of cookies as described here.</p>

        <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device by websites you visit. They are widely used to make websites work efficiently and to provide information to website owners. Cookies may be "session" cookies (deleted when you close your browser) or "persistent" cookies (retained for a set period).</p>

        <h2>2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

        <h3>Strictly Necessary Cookies</h3>
        <p>These cookies are essential for the website to function correctly. They cannot be disabled and do not require your consent. Examples include session management and security cookies.</p>

        <h3>Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p>We may use analytics tools to understand how visitors interact with our website (pages viewed, time on site, traffic sources). This data is aggregated and anonymised where possible. These cookies require your consent.</p>

        <h3>Preference Cookies</h3>
        <p>These cookies remember your choices — such as language or region preferences — to provide a more personalised experience.</p>

        <h2>3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p>Third-party services integrated into our site (such as embedded content, social sharing buttons, or analytics providers) may set their own cookies. We do not control these cookies. Please refer to the respective third-party privacy policies for details.</p>

        <h2>4. How to Manage Cookies</h2>
        <p>You can control and delete cookies at any time through your browser settings. Common browser options:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Chrome</strong>: Settings → Privacy and Security → Cookies and other site data</li>
          <li><strong>Firefox</strong>: Options → Privacy &amp; Security → Cookies and Site Data</li>
          <li><strong>Safari</strong>: Preferences → Privacy → Manage Website Data</li>
          <li><strong>Edge</strong>: Settings → Privacy, search, and services → Cookies</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Note that disabling cookies may affect the functionality of this website.</p>

        <h2>5. Do Not Track</h2>
        <p>Some browsers include a "Do Not Track" (DNT) feature. Our website does not currently respond to DNT signals, but we respect your preference as described in this Cookie Policy.</p>

        <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect any changes.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about our use of cookies, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@aitsgenesis.com">privacy@aitsgenesis.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
